{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "9e10609a-fd2f-4dd6-a6cb-4686e2363b99", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9e10609a-fd2f-4dd6-a6cb-4686e2363b99@3.pkg/1772597501931/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597502209", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9e10609a-fd2f-4dd6-a6cb-4686e2363b99@3.pkg/1772597501931/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597502209"}, "identifier": "9e10609a-fd2f-4dd6-a6cb-4686e2363b99", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>“潮汐窗口”通过动态调配资源直接提升服务响应效率，核心目标是优化群众办事体验，体现政府服务理念的升级。A正确。“潮汐窗口”不是监督权力行使，也没有让公民行使监督权。B、C错误。区政府不属于基层群众自治组织。D错误。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>(原创)天津市河西区政务服务办增设“潮汐窗口”，根据办事大厅人流量动态调整服务力量：当排队人数增多时，立即启用后备窗口分流；高峰期后恢复常规配置。该举措将群众平均等待时间缩短40%，特殊群体还可享受免排队服务。这样做旨在（　　）</p>\n", "title": "(原创)天津市河西区政务服务办增设“潮汐窗口”，根据办事大厅人流量动态调整服务力量：当排队人数增多时，立即启用后备窗口分流；高峰期后恢复常规配置。该举措将群众平均等待时间缩短40%，特殊群体还可享受免排队服务。这样做旨在（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9e10609a-fd2f-4dd6-a6cb-4686e2363b99@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754814305353", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_ide